results.name: Numerators of coefficients in a series solution to a certain ODE.
comment: Serial solution of ode (A.Gruzinov,2005): cos[t]f'[t]+sin[t]f''[t]+3/4 sin[t]f[t]=0, f[ -Pi/2]=1, f'[ -pi/2]=0, f[t]=1-3/8(t+Pi/2)^2-5/128(t+Pi/2)^4-193/15360(t+Pi/2)^4-... All coefficients (except 1) are negative, there is no simple recursion or other formula for the serial coefficients.
reference: A. Gruzinov, Power of axisymmetric pulsar, Phys. Rev. Lett. 94 (021101)(2005).
link: A. Gruzinov, Power of axisymmetric pulsar, arXiv:astro-ph/0407279, 2004.
results.author: _Zak Seidov_, Mar 31 2005
